<note style="-uslm-lc:I85" topic="transferOfFunctions" id="id778bd436-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Transfer of Functions</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Transfer of administrative functions of park, see note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s426">section 426 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
